## Smartmenu Views (customer-facing)
- `_showMenuContentStaff.html.erb` — staff menu view (uses `_showMenuitemStaff.erb`)
- `_showMenuContentCustomer.html.erb` — customer menu view (uses `_menu_section.html.erb`)
- `_showMenuitem.erb` — customer menu item card (card layout with image)
- `_showMenuitemHorizontal.html.erb` — customer menu item (horizontal layout)
- `_showMenuitemStaff.erb` — staff menu item (compact row with quick-add stepper)
- `_cart_bottom_sheet.html.erb` — customer cart (bottom sheet with peek/half/full states)
- `_showModals.erb` — shared modals (add-item, view-order, pay, etc.)
- `show.html.erb` — main smartmenu page (renders staff OR customer view based on role)

## Key Stimulus Controllers
- `state_controller.js` — central state manager (order, totals, restaurant context)
- `order_totals_controller.js` — order total calculations and display
- `bottom_sheet_controller.js` — cart bottom sheet (peek/half/full snap points)
- `quick_add_controller.js` — staff quantity stepper (+/- buttons)
- `ordering_controller.js` — order lifecycle management
- `square_payment_controller.js` — Square Web Payments SDK integration

## Database (105 tables)
- Schema: `db/schema.rb`
- Key tables: `ordrs`, `ordritems`, `ordractions`, `ordrparticipants`, `menus`, `menusections`, `menuitems`, `tablesettings`, `restaurants`, `users`, `employees`
- Materialized views: `dw_orders_mv` (analytics)
- Each ordritem is one row per unit (no quantity column yet)

