## Common Pitfalls
- Precompiled assets in `public/assets/` override live source files in dev — delete if JS changes aren't picked up
- API controllers must `skip_before_action` web callbacks (set_current_employee, set_permissions, etc.)
- `Menu` model conflicts with `Menu::` namespace for jobs — use `class Menu::MyJob` not `module Menu; class MyJob`
- Routes use non-RESTful names in places: check `config/routes.rb` before assuming path helpers
